
on armor change:
    set {_e} to enchantment from key "turtle:gliding_curse"
    player's chestplate is enchanted with {_e}
    player isn't gliding
    set player's gliding state to on
    tailwindBoost(player)

on toggling gliding:
    player is gliding
    set {_e} to enchantment from key "turtle:gliding_curse"
    player's chestplate is enchanted with {_e}
    cancel event
